OL,3,CVote to bring in extra parking charges
OL,4,Cfor SUVs and larger vehicles
OL,6,FCardiff could become the first city in
OL,7,Fthe UK to introduce more expensive
OL,8,Fparking charges for larger vehicles.
OL,10,FCouncillors will vote on plans today
OL,11,F(Thursday 16 October) to bring in a
OL,12,Fsurcharge for SUVs along with other
OL,13,Fparking measures as part of a new City
OL,14,FParking Plan.
OL,16,FThe report found that "large heavy
OL,17,Fvehicles take up more parking space
OL,18,Fand are a danger to other road users."
