OL,3,CVote to bring in extra parking charges
OL,4,Cfor SUVs and larger vehicles
OL,6,FIt also recommended that "a surcharge
OL,7,Ffor vehicles over 2,400kg Revenue
OL,8,FWeight will be introduced to encourage
OL,9,Fdrivers to switch to smaller vehicles.
OL,11,F"In time, this will be reduced to
OL,12,F2,000kg (for non-electric vehicles).
OL,14,F"Very large vehicles (vehicles over
OL,15,F3,500kg Revenue Weight) will not be
OL,16,Fentitled to permits."
