OL,3,CVote to bring in extra parking charges
OL,4,Cfor SUVs and larger vehicles
OL,6,FIt warns that "the higher the vehicle
OL,7,Ffront the more likely a person will be
OL,8,Fknocked under the car, rather than
OL,9,Fpushed to the side. And the risk to
OL,10,Fchildren is particularly stark."
OL,12,FOne study found that larger vehicles
OL,13,Fpose a far greater risk to vulnerable
OL,14,Froad users and showed children are
OL,15,Fthree times more likely to be killed
OL,16,Fin a collision with an SUV than a
OL,17,Fregular car.
OL,19,FHelen Edwards, whose son was hit by a
OL,20,Fcar last year, told councillors she
OL,21,Fwelcomes the plans.
