OL,6,FShe said: "Families like mine live
OL,7,Fevery day with the consequences of our
OL,8,Fstreets being dominated by ever-larger
OL,9,Fvehicles.
OL,11,F"This isn't about punishing drivers `
OL,12,Fit's about protecting children,
OL,13,Fpedestrians and our communities. If
OL,14,Fthis change helps even one family
OL,15,Favoid what we went through, it will be
OL,16,Fworth it.
OL,18,F"As a parent it's your worst nightmare
OL,19,Fto come out of your house and see your
OL,20,Fchild lying in the road.
